data.description: Welcome to 145 Brook Dr. NW - where spacious living meets thoughtful design! Step into a generously sized living area, creating an inviting space for relaxation and gatherings. The open-concept kitchen and dining areas seamlessly blend, offering not just a place to cook but a hub for shared meals and memorable moments.Both bedrooms in this home come complete with their own attached bathrooms, providing privacy and convenience. The primary bedroom is a retreat with its dedicated bathroom, ensuring a comfortable and personal space.Conveniently located, 145 Brook Dr. NW is just a short distance from shopping, restaurants, and all that Cleveland, Tennessee has to offer. Discover the perfect harmony of ample living space and thoughtful layouts at 145 Brook Dr. NW. Schedule a showing to experience the ease and comfort this home has to offer.
